#

Honey Glazed Balsamic Chicken

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

DinnerMain CourseComfort Food

Description

Succulent chicken thighs glazed with a sweet and tangy honey balsamic sauce, served with roasted vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Thighs: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Mixed Vegetables (Zucchini, Bell Peppers, Carrots): 2 cups
